name: Classic Address Stamp
description:
PCG Classic Address Stamps provide the best ROI for a closing gift on the market. Our proprietary process incorporates your marketing information on the front of every stamp casing. This information will NEVER rub or scratch off! It is not a label or piece of paper. This stamp will last thousands of impressions and your client will never get rid of it. That means, your client will have your name, phone number and email at their fingertips when they are ready to move or refer you to a friend.

*Address Stamps have a onetime $45 set up fee to develop the artwork on the front of the stamp casing. Please send us your photo, logo and any marketing information that you would like to appear on the front of your stamp casing. Please submit your attachments in a .jpeg or .TIFF file format in 300 dpi resolution or better and e-mail to: artwork@perfectclosinggift.com. You will receive a full color artwork proof within 1 to 3 business days. Please, respond to the e-mail with any necessary changes. We will make any required changes and re-send an updated artwork proof for final acceptance. Credit card payment for the artwork fee can be made over the phone when artwork is submitted 805-481-9787 x110

name: Large Glass Cutting Board
description: PCG Large Glass Cutting Boards (12 x 15) are antibacterial, dishwasher safe, shatter resistant and perfect for all food types. When they are not busy preparing the daily meal, these beautiful cutting boards will be displayed as kitchen décor. Select from one of our 30 specially designed templates or upload your custom photo.

name: Small Glass Cutting Board
description: PCG Small Glass cutting boards (8 x 10) can be personalized from 30 specially designed templates or you can upload any custom photo*. This board is the ideal size for a small home, condo, wet bar or as a serving tray for charcuterie. The best thing about our tempered glass boards is that they will be left out on the client's counter as home decor when they are not in use keeping you top of mind. Dishwasher safe, anti-bacterial and shatter resistant.

name: Marble Wood Cheese Board
description: The PCG Marble with Acacia Wood Cheese board is an exceptional gift which pairs functionality with classic home décor elements. This gorgeous, kitchen décor item with your subtle marketing will stay out on the client's counter when it is not in use - it will not be put away in a drawer! That means you can market to your client AND their friends and family

name: Marble Wood Coasters
description: PCG Marble with Acacia Wood Coaster Sets are a great standalone gift or as a compliment to the matching cheese board. The trendy mixed materials offer an upscale look and will be used on a regular basis by friends and family alike.

name: Charcuterie Plank
description: PCG’s Maple Charcuterie Plank is sure to impress any client who loves to entertain (or just loves cheese)! Handcrafted from 100% natural maple and finished with an artisan teak oil, this rustic farmhouse serving plank is one of the highest rated cheese boards on the market. Built with quality and craftsmanship, this serving plank makes a gorgeous display piece when not in use, adding warmth and character to your client’s home.

name: Maple Cutting Board
description: Maple wood, which is light in color and full of subtle grain marks, makes and excellent complement to your client's kitchen. Maple is a hard wood which resists scarring and provides a natural protection against microbial contamination.

name: Bamboo Cheese Board w/ 3 Tools
description: The PCG Bamboo Cheese board with Three Cheese Tools is the luxury choice for serving cheese while entertaining. Each gift is made with a caramel colored, naturally sustainable bamboo cutting board base. The bamboo is topped by a removable tempered Pyrex cutting board that doubles as a serving tray. This special gift includes a set of 3 Cheese tools in a hidden drawer for different kinds of cheese varietals.

name: Slate Cheese Board
description: Our charcoal slate cheese boards offer a beautifully rustic, organic surface to match any type of household. From a farmhouse styled home to a bachelor pad, these slate cutting boards are sure to make a statement.

name: Slate Coaster Set
description: Slate is a very popular material trending in today's kitchens. The natural streamlined look complements rustic and contemporary home design in both style and color. The set of four 4”x4” coasters are equipped with cork feet for furniture protection.

name: Laguiole Steak Knife Set
description: PCG Laguiole Steak Knives are renowned for quality and tradition that dates from the 19th century. Made in Laguiole, France the set of six stainless-steel knives comes with ivory acrylic handles that includes beautiful Platine detailing down the spine of each blade.  Each gift is presented in a personalized presentation box that is monogrammed for your client and includes your marketing or two-line message of gratitude (or logo). Inside each gift set is a Certificate of Authenticity.

name: Santoku Knife Set
description: The Santoku knives are hand forged in Germany with the highest quality carbon stainless steel for exceptional durability. Each blade is laser pricision measured to guarantee world class sharpness. This beautiful set comes in a personalized bamboo presentation box. The removable lid doubles as a cutting board.

name: Rustic Lantern
description: Be the focal point of your client's home with our captivating personalized rustic lanterns. The delightful flicker of a candle illuminates your client's name.

name: Dog Treat Jar
description: Give your client's furry friend a special treat on closing day. This refillable treat jar is personalized with your client's pup's name & comes with 18 matching peanut butter personalized cookies!

name: Cottage Ornament
description: Give your client a charming wooden cottage to commemorate the purchase of their home

name: Glass Ornament
description: Glass Holiday Ornaments are a sentimental keepsake that your client will place on their tree every year. This is a great way to touch this year’s clients to say Thank You. Available in four shapes, personalize each ornament with the family name, year, and your holiday wishes.

name: Welcome Home Doormat
description: Our classically inspired coir doormat knows how to make an entrance and keep the foyer clean. These mats are manufactured in the USA from durable dense natural coir fiber (outer husk of coconut shells). Using coir helps scrape shoes clean with lasting endurance. Each fiber is inserted into an all-weather vinyl backing to increase durability and help prevent shifting and movement.  To ensure a long-lasting product, the personalization on the mat is flocked instead of painted to resist fading. These mats are stain, rot, and mildew resistant, weather tolerant and can absorb moisture.

name: Thirsty Stone Coasters
description: PCG Thirsty Coasters are perfect for everyday use in your client’s home. Our set of four 4” x 4” coasters are made from natural sandstone which absorbs moisture and condensation. Cork backing protects furniture.
